    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1944-04-14T21:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1944-04-14T21:00:00-05:00" n="731"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d731">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.544/67: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Gauss</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Chungking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1944-04-15T09:00:00+07:00"
                            >April 15, 1944—9 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received 9:15 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>658. Department’s 310, March 7, 6 p.m. Copy of draft revision of copyright law
                    being airmailed.<note n="6" xml:id="d731fn6">Not printed.</note> Understood to
                    have been passed by Legislative Yuan March 31 but not yet promulgated. No
                    radical changes made in existing law.</p>
                <p>According to records of Economic Affairs Ministry and Legislative Yuan, no
                    amendment to company law has been promulgated. Regulations governing special
                    limited corporations were promulgated March 1940. Copy being airmailed.<note
                        n="6" xml:id="d731fn7">Not printed.</note> Registration fees were increased
                    900% June 9, 1943.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Gauss</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
